<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Facture</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-alpha.6/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-rwoIResjU2yc3z8GV/NPeZWAv56rSmLldC3R/AZzGRnGxQQKnKkoFVhFQhNUwEyJ" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <style>
    body {
      font-size: 0.6em;
    }

    h6 {
      font-size: 1em;
    }

    .container {
      width: 21cm;
    }

    .invoice {
      background: #fff;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 50px;
    }

    .logo {
      height: 50px;
      width: auto;
    }

    .document-type {
      text-align: right;
      color: #444;
    }

    .conditions {
      font-size: 0.7em;
      color: #666;
    }

    .bottom-page {
      font-size: 0.7em;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="invoice">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-7">
          <img src="<%= icon %>" class="logo" alt="logo.png" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-5">
          <h1 class="document-type display-4">FACTURE</h1>
          <p class="text-right"><strong>Référence facture</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-7">
          <p class="addressMySam">
            <strong>OmniBetter</strong><br />
            support@omnibetter.fr<br>
            11 avenue des chasseurs<br>
            75017 Paris
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-5">
          <br /><br /><br />
          <p class="addressDriver">
            <strong>Information client</strong><br>
            <%= user?.name %><br>
            <%= user?.email %><br>
            <%= user?.address %>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <br />
      <table class="table table-striped">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Ordinateur</th>
            <th>Quantité</th>
            <th class="text-right">Montant Unité</th>
            <th class="text-right">Montant Total</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% items.forEach((desktop, index) => { %>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <%= desktop.title %><br>
              <%= desktop.assembly %>
            </td>
            <td class="text-center"><%= desktop.quantity %></td>
            <td class="text-right"><%= desktop.price %> &euro;</td>
            <td class="text-right"><%= (desktop.totalAmount / 100).toFixed(2).replace('.', ',').replace(/\B(?=(\d{3})+(?!\d))/g, '.') %> &euro;</td>
          </tr>
          <% }) %>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <%= delivery.name %>
            </td>
            <td class="text-center">1</td>
            <td class="text-right"><%= delivery.price %> &euro;</td>
            <td class="text-right"><%= delivery.price %> &euro;</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-8">
        </div>
        <div class="col-4">
          <table class="table table-sm text-right">
            <tr>
              <td>Remise</td>
              <td class="text-right"><%= total.promotion %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Total HT</strong></td>
              <td class="text-right"><%= total.withoutTax %> &euro;</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>TVA 20%</td>
              <td class="text-right"><%= total.tax %> &euro;</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Total TTC</strong></td>
              <td class="text-right"><%= total.totalAmount %> &euro;</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="conditions">
        Merci infiniment pour votre confiance en nos services. En cas de besoin, n'hésitez pas à contacter notre équipe de support dédiée, soit en visitant notre site web à l'adresse https://omnibetter.fr, soit en nous envoyant un email à support@omnibetter.fr. Nous sommes là pour vous aider. <br><br>
        Nous n'accordons pas d'escompte en cas de paiement anticipé.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>